Brett Climo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brett_Climo 0 Brett Climo (born 26 September 1964 in Sydney, New South Wales, Australia) is an Australian actor, best known for his television soap opera roles, but also has appeared in films (feature length and made for TV features).
